<main role="main">
	<div class="page-header">
	<h1>The power of good design</h1>
			<div class="intro-text"><span>Dieter Rams’s ideology, engrained within Vitsœ</span>
				</div>
	</div>
	<div id="content" class="cf">
		

<div class="container">

		<div class="introductions borderless margin-below-2">

			<div class="introductions-title">
				
					<h2>Good design at Vitsœ</h2>
				
			</div>
			<div class="introductions-media">
				<figure>
					<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 2100px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 2100px, (min-width: 2120px) 2100px, (min-width: 1060px) 1050px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1704/crop169/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1704/crop169/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1704/crop169/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1704/crop169/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1704/crop169/1050.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1704/crop169/1920.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1704/crop169/2880.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1704/crop169/1050.jpg" alt="Lounge chair and ottoman, comfortable reading chair and ottoman, designer, modern, high back in red leather. Off-white shell. 620 Chair. Dieter Rams designs. Hand made by Vitsœ. Library shelving system, modular bookshelves" />
					<figcaption></figcaption>
				</figure>
			</div>
			<div class="introductions-content">
				<p>Here at Vitsœ we stand for the inordinate power of good design in everything we do: designing thoughtfully, responsibly and intelligently for our company, our furniture and the many people who share a profound interest in all of our tomorrows.</p>

<p>For over 60 years, Vitsœ has worked continuously with Dieter Rams. He still improves his designs to this day and is often cited by a new generation as a key influence on their work that is shaping the 21st century.</p>

			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="quote margin-below">
			<div class="quote-content">
				<div class="quote-text"><p>“In 1957 I began to develop a storage system that formed the basis of the company Vitsœ, which was founded in 1959. Thus the ideology behind my design is engrained within the company.”</p>
</div>
				<div class="quote-author">
					<div class="quote-author-title">Dieter Rams</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="text-block">
			<div class="text-block-title">
				<h2>Ten principles for good design</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="text-block-content margin-below">
				<p>Back in the late 1970s, Dieter Rams was becoming increasingly concerned by the state of the world around him: “An impenetrable confusion of forms, colours and noises.”</p>

<p>Aware that he was a significant contributor to that world, he asked himself an important question: is my design good design?</p>

<p>His answer is expressed in his ten principles for good design.</p>

			</div>
			<figure class="text-block-primary-image">
				<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 1420px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 1420px, (min-width: 2120px) 1420px, (min-width: 1060px) 710px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1328/crop169/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1328/crop169/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1328/crop169/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1328/crop169/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1328/crop169/1050.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1328/crop169/1050.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1328/crop169/1050.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/2000/1328/crop169/710.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams, Vitsœ&amp;#8217;s furniture designer. Photograph by Abisag Tüllmann" />
				<figcaption>
					Vitsœ’s designer, Dieter Rams. Photograph by Abisag Tüllmann
					
				</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="border-above principle">
			<div class="principle-number extra-indent">1</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design is innovative</h2>
				<p>The possibilities for innovation are not, by any means, exhausted. Technological development is always offering new opportunities for innovative design. But innovative design always develops in tandem with innovative technology, and can never be an end in itself.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 2120px) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) 410px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/139/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/139/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/139/crops/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/139/crops/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/139/crops/710.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/139/crops/710.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/139/crops/710.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/139/crops/410.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. TP 1 radio/phono combination, 1959, designed by Dieter Rams for Braun" />
				<figcaption>TP 1 radio/phono combination, 1959, by Dieter Rams for Braun</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-number">2</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design makes a product useful</h2>
				<p>A product is bought to be used. It has to satisfy certain criteria, not only functional, but also psychological and aesthetic. Good design emphasizes the usefulness of a product whilst disregarding anything that could possibly detract from it.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 2120px) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) 410px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/140/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/140/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/140/crops/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/140/crops/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/140/crops/710.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/140/crops/710.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/140/crops/710.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/140/crops/410.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. MPZ 21 multipress citrus juicer, 1972, designed by Dieter Rams and Jürgen Greubel for Braun" />
				<figcaption>MPZ 21 multipress citrus juicer, 1972, by Dieter Rams and Jürgen Greubel for Braun</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-number">3</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design is aesthetic</h2>
				<p>The aesthetic quality of a product is integral to its usefulness because products we use every day affect our person and our well-being. But only well-executed objects can be beautiful.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 2120px) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) 410px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/141/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/141/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/141/crops/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/141/crops/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/141/crops/710.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/141/crops/710.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/141/crops/710.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/141/crops/410.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. RT 20 tischsuper radio, 1961, designed by Dieter Rams for Braun" />
				<figcaption>RT 20 tischsuper radio, 1961, by Dieter Rams for Braun</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-number">4</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design makes a product understandable</h2>
				<p>It clarifies the product’s structure. Better still, it can make the product talk. At best, it is self-explanatory.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 2120px) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) 410px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/142/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/142/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/142/crops/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/142/crops/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/142/crops/710.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/142/crops/710.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/142/crops/710.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/142/crops/410.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. T 1000 world receiver, 1963, designed by Dieter Rams for Braun" />
				<figcaption>T 1000 world receiver, 1963, by Dieter Rams for Braun</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-number">5</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design is unobtrusive</h2>
				<p>Products fulfilling a purpose are like tools. They are neither decorative objects nor works of art. Their design should therefore be both neutral and restrained, to leave room for the user’s self-expression.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 2120px) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) 410px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/143/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/143/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/143/crops/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/143/crops/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/143/crops/710.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/143/crops/710.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/143/crops/710.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/143/crops/410.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. Cylindric T 2 lighter, 1968, designed by Dieter Rams for Braun" />
				<figcaption>Cylindric T 2 lighter, 1968, by Dieter Rams for Braun</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-number">6</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design is honest</h2>
				<p>It does not make a product more innovative, powerful or valuable than it really is. It does not attempt to manipulate the consumer with promises that cannot be kept.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 2120px) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) 410px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/144/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/144/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/144/crops/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/144/crops/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/144/crops/710.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/144/crops/710.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/144/crops/710.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/144/crops/410.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. L 450 flat loudspeaker, TG 60 reel-to-reel tape recorder and TS 45 control unit, 1962-64, designed by Dieter Rams for Braun" />
				<figcaption>L 450 flat loudspeaker, TG 60 reel-to-reel tape recorder and TS 45 control unit, 1962-64, by Dieter Rams for Braun</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-number">7</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design is long-lasting</h2>
				<p>It avoids being fashionable and therefore never appears antiquated. Unlike fashionable design, it lasts many years – even in today’s throwaway society.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<a href="/us/620"><img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 340px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 340px, (min-width: 2120px) 340px, (min-width: 1060px) 170px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/297/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/297/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/297/crops/170.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/297/crops/170.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/297/crops/170.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/297/crops/170.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/297/crops/170.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/297/crops/170.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. Lounge chair, 620 Chair Programme. Dieter Rams designs. Hand made by Vitsœ" /></a>
				<figcaption><a href="/us/620">620 Chair Program</a>, 1962, by Dieter Rams for Vitsœ</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-number">8</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design is thorough down to the last detail</h2>
				<p>Nothing must be arbitrary or left to chance. Care and accuracy in the design process show respect towards the user.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 2120px) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) 410px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/145/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/145/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/145/crops/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/145/crops/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/145/crops/710.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/145/crops/710.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/145/crops/710.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/145/crops/410.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. ET 66 calculator, 1987, by Dietrich Lubs for Braun" />
				<figcaption>ET 66 calculator, 1987, by Dietrich Lubs for Braun</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-number">9</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design is environmentally-friendly</h2>
				<p>Design makes an important contribution to the preservation of the environment. It conserves resources and minimizes physical and visual pollution throughout the lifecycle of the product.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<a href="/us/606"><img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 2120px) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) 410px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/148/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/148/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/148/crops/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/148/crops/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/148/crops/710.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/148/crops/710.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/148/crops/710.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/148/crops/410.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. Modular shelving, 606 Universal Shelving System with drawer cabinets. Made and sold by Vitsœ" /></a>
				<figcaption><a href="/us/606">606 Universal Shelving System</a>, 1960, by Dieter Rams for Vitsœ</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-number extra-indent">10</div>
			<div class="principle-content">
				<h2>Good design is as little design as possible</h2>
				<p>Less, but better – because it concentrates on the essential aspects, and the products are not burdened with non-essentials.</p>

<p>Back to purity, back to simplicity.</p>

				
			</div>
			<figure class="principle-image">
				<img sizes="(min-width: 1060px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) and (min-resolution: 1.9) 820px, (min-width: 2120px) 820px, (min-width: 1060px) 410px, 100vw" srcset="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/149/crops/50.jpg 50w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/149/crops/170.jpg 170w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/149/crops/410.jpg 410w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/149/crops/710.jpg 710w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/149/crops/710.jpg 1050w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/149/crops/710.jpg 1920w, https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/149/crops/710.jpg 2880w" src="https://d2lsod3xpjaepj.cloudfront.net/files/assets/1000/149/crops/410.jpg" alt="Dieter Rams designs. L 2 speaker, 1958, designed by Dieter Rams for Braun" />
				<figcaption>L 2 speaker, 1958, by Dieter Rams for Braun</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

